Text.Value: AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set
Upon completion of this training, you will learn how to effectively operate the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set by achieving the following objectives:
• Identify the characteristics, capabilities, and features of the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set.
• Conduct Preventive Maintenance Checks and Services (PMCS) and preoperational procedures on the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set.
• Employ the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set.
• Perform Troubleshooting Procedures on the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set.
• Perform Troubleshooting Procedures on the AN/UDR-14 Radiac Set.
